---
title: Seared Rump Steak & Mustardy Greens with Garlic-Parsley Butter & Mash
description: Long after you finish this humble dinner of steak and greens, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple addition of tangy wholegrain mustard cooked into the veggies. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease of life.

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with broccolini. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-rump-steak-mustard-greens-33967e41.jpg
